Communicated by:
ProMED

[In July 2022, Russia reported 2 outbreaks of Lumpy Skin disease in Tuva. The event was resolved on 29 Aug 2022. See latest report on 22 Sep 2022 at https://wahis.woah.org/#/in-review/4554

